{"tid":1283954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【表達訴求不能停】【香港版東德起義】 7月7日！","createTime":"2019-07-04T03:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T05:23:39.000Z","uid":87915,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bf2250125d77561b42a61b6a52abca0e4be10d8f","tid":1283954,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:35:00.000Z","msg":"大家要不停宣傳    唔好比佢停<br />\n每星期一次都要做<br />\n<br />\n可以參考 東德起義：<br />\n<br />\n「週一示威（德語：Montagsdemonstrationen）是反對德意志民主共和國（東德）的一連串和平反政府遊行，於1989年至1990年間每週一傍晚舉行。<br />\n<br />\n示威首先於萊比錫開始，然後德累斯頓、哈雷、卡爾&middot;馬克思城、馬德堡、普勞恩、阿恩施塔特、羅斯托克、波茨坦和施威林等地人民加入。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">群眾壓力引致柏林圍牆於11月9日倒下，標誌着東德政權的衰亡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWvGAqw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWvGAqw.png&h=82a2bdc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油‼️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------<br />\n我無野講 我唔解鎖 我要搵律師 唔好兇我 我投訴你"},{"pid":"3ea8d3ba5f947a1762a933d9c4eaab680344aa4b","tid":1283954,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"自推 !"},{"pid":"77ba1f91e758c3f5f639e872f35d2c04e3ab9b9b","tid":1283954,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"再推！"},{"pid":"533ec08f2ada4379e4a1b3baf86b4f4252c54940","tid":1283954,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"不停推‼️"},{"pid":"7a1243a5d1ee681f6ceb6e1249417f63e5e7f674","tid":1283954,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"推上熱門！"},{"pid":"db112b86db5546a5b16f1e745934eb40a26139b5","tid":1283954,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:38:24.000Z","msg":"無人推就自己推！"},{"pid":"6d8b157be974e3f18bb4e2d54948f60eda90f898","tid":1283954,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":